5
00:00:19.179 --> 00:00:20.449
Aku ingin berkeluarga.

6
00:00:21.309 --> 00:00:24.550
Kurasa aku bisa hidup bahagia bersamamu.

7
00:00:26.849 --> 00:00:28.589
Aku memenangi kontes.

8
00:00:29.449 --> 00:00:30.489
Tapi

9
